---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="CSS Grid 实战笔记" description="用 CSS Grid 重构布局的实践经验。">
  <article>
    <a href="/blog" class="text-xs text-text-dim no-underline hover:text-white transition-colors inline-block mb-8">← 返回 Blog</a>
    <div class="flex gap-2 mb-5">
      <span class="font-mono text-[11px] px-3.5 py-1 rounded-full bg-pink-500/10 text-pink-400 border border-pink-500/20">CSS</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white leading-snug mb-3 tracking-tight">
      CSS Grid 实战笔记
    </h2>
    <div class="font-mono text-[13px] text-text-dim mb-12">2026 年 3 月 20 日</div>
    <div class="text-base text-[#d4d4d8] leading-relaxed space-y-6">
      <p>用 CSS Grid 重构了整个布局，比 Flexbox 更适合二维排版场景。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <a href="/blog" class="text-xs text-text-dim no-underline hover:text-white transition-colors">← 返回 Blog</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
